32:31.165 --> 32:39.738
was taken. And we established our first point 
there of freight being moved by our aircraft in the

32:46.475 --> 32:49.961
Cherbourg. And then the next point that I moved 
into was into Paris. But at Cherbourg it was

32:56.513 --> 33:01.902
basically move in as much military supplies as 
fast as possible. Flying the essentials.

33:05.935 --> 33:08.357
Everything else still came in by boat and by 
lighter. But the essentials were flown in.

