33:19.788 --> 33:22.150
you fly in? Parts. Mechanical parts. And were you 
flying the old bombers or were you flying

33:25.513 --> 33:28.715
anything? Anything that we had. Most of, by that 
time, the we were pretty well equipped with C-47.

