Another officer now went in and made the 
assessment. What's the difference now? I'm not

34:23.309 --> 34:24.611
quite clear on that. What do you mean the other 
aircraft were going to... The inter-theater from

34:27.995 --> 34:32.680
Paris back to the United States. Oh, okay. The big, 
which is now MAC. We were strictly theater. Okay,

34:40.389 --> 34:42.672
okay. And they, by the time we knew that we... 
