39:40.989 --> 39:56.352
screwed up, it was based on a table of organization 
equipment that was put together for the HUP in

39:57.074 --> 40:00.417
India. And TO had six officers authorized, and we 
had 36 officers.

40:12.609 --> 40:20.256
Any time you do that, all you do is you rob 30 
authorizations from your subordinates. And it

40:20.276 --> 40:23.419
makes promotions pretty damn rough. I was sitting 
there as a major in the lieutenant colonel's slot.

40:26.355 --> 40:29.999
What a way in the world to get promoted. So 
everything is eaten up, you know. Then they

40:32.381 --> 40:36.546
started holding us to authorization. Now, can you 
tell me about the conditions in Paris? You must

40:39.850 --> 40:41.271
have gone into Paris. And about the people, how 
they treated you.

40:47.998 --> 40:52.123
Well,

40:47.998 --> 40:52.123
the Parisians There are French people and there 
are Parisians.

41:03.940 --> 41:16.157
The Frenchman, individually, is one of the nicest 
guys that I think you'll ever want to know.

41:16.177 --> 41:19.782
Collectively, they're a bunch of milk hounds. 
They get, we were talking about spirit and emotion

41:19.802 --> 41:23.427
earlier. They get all wrapped up and they're just 
too damn easy to get let off on the wrong track or

41:23.643 --> 41:34.073
something like that. We had no problems with them 
because, again, we were

41:34.093 --> 41:53.633
the big liberators and a lot of them knew it even 
though we sat back and a number of units like us were

41:34.093 --> 41:53.633
in there, no big U.S. unit with great big generals 
came in until after De Gaulle did. De Gaulle made

42:00.921 --> 42:07.589
the sweep into Paris and took all of the glory and 
everything. Even though we had units already in

42:08.710 --> 42:10.412
there. They didn't put generals in to make parades 
and claim the victory. They let De Gaulle come in.

42:17.920 --> 42:22.485
But the Frenchmen knew who were in there. Because 
At that time, de Gaulle still didn't have France

42:23.279 --> 42:28.526
completely under his wings. He was still a little

42:28.666 --> 42:44.908
questionable.

