We had some misgivings with some of their military 
are owning it. We lived in a fabulous, the officers

42:55.411 --> 43:07.264
lived in a fabulous big house out on the edge of the 
border balloon, which is the fashionable part of

42:55.411 --> 43:07.264
Paris. And directly across the street from the 
Gauls residence. And every once in a while,

43:20.080 --> 43:48.737
security would get a little concerned about our 
conduct or what was going on and come over and try to

43:20.080 --> 43:48.737
quiet us down or something like that and so our 
provost marshal was always having to remind them

