the relations between the French and the American

44:05.158 --> 44:14.767
soldiers, as far as you knew, were rather 
strained? No. Friendly? Oh, they were friendly,

44:18.070 --> 44:19.652
sure. We're just in an isolated situation here 
where if I was guarding the galleys, it would scare

44:20.223 --> 44:25.951
the hell out of me, too. Sure. Absolutely.

