45:28.140 --> 45:38.475
day with my half, and then when Henry went back out 
the next day, it was run by military police. So we

45:39.215 --> 45:41.839
only got two days haul of coal out of there. But we 
had officers and men hauling coal like they came

45:41.899 --> 45:49.972
out of West Virginia because coal was in real short 
